{"tid":1074063,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人幾樣打邊爐好少人食但係好撚正既食材","createTime":"2019-03-23T06:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T08:55:47.000Z","uid":171273,"like":4,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e2e5a4a1d4b8ca9c60f9d208b5ad88cbddbb6e","tid":1074063,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"1. 切片牛油果<br />\n有時見平會買 記得買長身既 粒核會細D多肉食D<br />\n買返黎切厚片去皮 淥10零秒食得<br />\n點豉油食有少少似鯇魚片口感 三文魚味 但係無果陣三文魚腥味<br />\n次次都比人搶哂<br />\n<br />\n2. 棉花糖<br />\n呢個係有次燒野食用剩 打邊爐本身諗住玩野<br />\n點知發現幾正 棉花糖中間多窿窿 索哂D湯底香味 又有本身甜味<br />\n淥一淥就食得 太耐會融哂落兜湯 <br />\nbtw棉花糖要湯底本身香先好食(例如藥饍/ 椰香)"},{"pid":"e84c724fa71b34a8153c1584a23cfcb62a03b871","tid":1074063,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"btw其實牛油果粒核淥熟都可以食<br />\n食落似栗子"},{"pid":"35961a688950ca66814c926dd9194128473435e9","tid":1074063,"uid":207702,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"雞子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d65822110a29d00d931db69ffde6a0e9316af3","tid":1074063,"uid":171273,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35961a688950ca66814c926dd9194128473435e9","tid":1074063,"uid":207702,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"雞子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"db4052262e8ad7d0f6618e788a9af250e4595430","tid":1074063,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"三六<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca78d849f7e194936565c3f492328d37906b79e5","tid":1074063,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"冬陰公+棉花糖 諗起都扯扯地"},{"pid":"d9616a2d87a12d3f2097a0ccbed9e6c7515ea919","tid":1074063,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2